title: 21-Day Meditation Challenge: Miraculous Relationships by Oprah W
description:
Oprah Winfrey and Deepak Chopra guide you on a meditation journey to the heart of true love, in "Miraculous Relationships," the newest release from the internationally popular Chopra Center 21-Day Meditation Challenge series. Discover the wonder that exists within and then watch all of your relationships unfold effortlessly, easily, and miraculously.

Learn to embrace your true essence, expand your understanding of divine relationship, and experience an unparalleled connection to your world around.  Discover how to prepare for, create, and live a life filled with everyday miracles.
